scatter thou the peoples that delíght in wár; 31 Then shall the princes come óut of Égypt;
the Morians’ land shall soon stretch out her hánds unto Gód. 32 Sing unto God, O ye kíngdoms of the éarth;
O sing praises únto the Lórd; 33 Who sitteth in the heavens over all, fróm the begínning:
